Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I wasn't supposed to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That beautiful young man I\Nsaw that night, one year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who see Johan must die. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard three shots. I got scared and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that Dr. Tenma had been shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but the next day's newspaper said that a man named\NJunkers had been shot three times and had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his doing, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you should shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shoot me, you can't get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get the photos\Nof Johan as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think will\Nhappen if you shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The photos will automatically be handed over\Nto men from the confederate police agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the photos,\Ntell me where Tenma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're showing quite a bit of guts, but\Nin reality, you can barely stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fascinating woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Tenma doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he's a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,though he's an underground one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a man who clawed his way\Nup to Number 2 in the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss there attacked the man, and\Nhe got away with just a few injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is helping that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in a mansion near Füssen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:41.09,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,550)\pos(360,340)}Of Men and Dining
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be lunch time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"What"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, because the weather is so nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd have lunch outside today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, bring the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds are healing nicely.\NYou should get some sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you really saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your surgery was perfect, even in that\Nrun-down hospital in that podunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound on your head was just a graze,\Nand your leg only had a piercing wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your anterior tibial artery was fine.\NYou were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look what I cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what you might guess, Heckel's\Ncooking is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N"Despite what you might guess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is young duck cooked in a Marengo\Nstyle, but the sauce is what makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only made at the three-star\Nrestaurant "Le Petit Besson."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your explanations are always so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be even better\Nwith some soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you and soy sauce? Do you\Nhave a problem with my flavoring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A dining table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what a dining table is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I did whatever it took to get money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything to get more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw away my parents; I made\Nmy siblings into my enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and children were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But all I wanted was to have\Na dining table like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Money can drive people mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard about this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, there was a  "bank" created in Germany that monopolized all the black market funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Their work was spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If money made from illegal activities was\Npassed through the "bank," the money\Nwould become clean and legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about money laundering, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a real bank, they ran a business\Nand allowed people to borrow money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That organization became larger\Nand larger in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They made millions in just five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However... this year, the top man who ran the\Norganization disappeared all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaos beyond comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The people that were left started\Nfighting over the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them died, and that\Norganization was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If only they'd all sat around a\Ntable and eaten together...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That top man who disappeared all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a student somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumor is that the man... no,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the kid that created the organization five years\Nago was only fifteen years old at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What could a kid like that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if he was experimenting in\Nan adult's game of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,like a child playing with a line of ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where was it? This underground bank...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The organization was based in Düsseldorf,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but the top man gave orders from different\Nplaces as he moved from city to city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the last order before\Nhe disappeared come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details, but I've heard that the men\Nwho had their eyes on the money left for Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Doctor? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's invite the man at the\Nbottom of the hill for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but his job is to be my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The world already thinks that you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone's still going\Nto try to get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to continue living a lifestyle that\Nrequires that you're constantly guarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worked for me for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, go call Helmut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So his name is Helmut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Tell him that his duty as\Nmy bodyguard is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my last friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to come to this table so we can\Ndiscuss what will happen from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Helmut! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's up at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to kill him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happened to Helmut, my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the people who're after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but someone is headed for this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Helmut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to run away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But your leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the shot come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. More importantly,\Nyou need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! If you stay here, they'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't. You have to\Nhide in the thicket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't intend to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, but that guy's probably\Nat the mansion by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't make it to the mansion\Nwithout passing through this route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been all over this hill. All the other paths\Nare like cliffs, and you can't go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we stand guard here, he won't be\Nable to make it any further up the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's after Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Are you a friend of Tenma's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me warn you... I'm not an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go tell Tenma to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But old lady... err, I mean, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're bleeding pretty badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma probably heard the gunshot\Nfrom before and is coming to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand that Roberto\Nis going to {\i1}kill {\i0} Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we run, you'll lose more\Nblood and die, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I'm not old!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, ol... miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be, since you're\Nwilling to get shot to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You love him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you his lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watch over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you {\i0} like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto! If you're thinking of shooting\Nme from the bushes, you should stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The photos of Johan that you want will go\Nto the confederate police agency if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want those photos,\Nget the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you've found his weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He might not fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run and save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do that. Tenma will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He will! Tenma will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never come save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come any closer, he'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's after your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That voice! It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This old lady knows you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been shot and is bleeding badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to hand you\Nover to the police alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can rot in a cell in shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,while you regret ever throwing me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter! Can you hear me, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell where the bad man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell where he's shooting from!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd come for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injury is healing nicely,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're healthy enough to eat\Nout in this nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who shot you was a professional assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was totally calm when he tried\Nto break into this cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one way to get in, and considering\Nhow many security systems and armed men I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it was obvious he didn't stand a\Nchance in an all-out fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So he used you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He used me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He predicted that no one except a lone woman\Naimlessly stopping by to visit could ever get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you betrayed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when his plan fell apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He left?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He wasn't in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is young duck cooked in a Marengo style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I just made the recipe up from what I tasted,\NI don't know if it will be good or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing that makes you lucky is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Dr. Tenma treated your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He had some interest in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's have some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you, just like I did for a long time, have\Nforgotten what it was like to have a meal like this.
